This map was created originally by Cleav420

This is #10 map i have made.

This map has alot of places go hide.

I will tell you some of the things that are in this map.
There is a boat in a garage that you can get into and ride around areas.
And you can shoot towers down into the water.

As well there are rooftops and freeway signs you can try to jump to.
There is a crain holding a freeway sign as well to climb up and own zombies.

Now i cant tell you every place to go and hide in this map.
You will need to download it and try on your own ROFL!!

But this map is crazy if you dont like to run as hell map.
Then you will never have fun ROFL :)

So enjoy the map and please leave comment about map.

Also if any one likes the few maps i made you can x-fire me @ cleav420
Or visit my ventrilo for info on how to better my maps,
Or even work with me together on one of my maps.
Thx .:{Cleav420}:.
